            <h1>Tasks To Earn Points:</h1>
            <div>
                <h2>Electricity Bill Reduction</h2>
                <div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Challenge yourself to lower your electricity bill compared to the previous month.</li>
                        <li>Implement energy-saving practices such as turning off lights and appliances when not in use, using energy-efficient lighting and appliances, and adjusting your thermostat to conserve energy.</li>
                        <li>Once you've reduced your electricity bill, submit proof (such as a screenshot of your utility statement) to earn points.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <h2>Public Transport Usage</h2>
                <div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Opt for public transportation for your daily commute or leisure activities instead of using a personal vehicle.</li>
                        <li>Whether it's taking the bus, train, tram, or subway, choose public transport options to reduce your carbon footprint and ease traffic congestion.</li>
                        <li>Save your public transport ticket or receipt and submit it as proof to earn points.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <h2>Water Bill Reduction</h2>
                <div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Take steps to decrease your water consumption and lower your water bill from the previous month.</li>
                        <li>Practice water-saving habits such as fixing leaky faucets, installing water-saving devices, and using water-efficient appliances.</li>
                        <li>After successfully reducing your water bill, submit proof (such as a photo of your reduced water usage) to earn points.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
